{"tid":1680580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[黃定光] 議員：示威者扮記者向警掟磚","createTime":"2019-10-29T02:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T03:12:38.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0134deeaf97119f67795c829e83ac87b14396435","tid":1680580,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:06:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%AE%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%9F%E7%A3%9A-214500681.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2589%25AE%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258E%259F%25E7%25A3%259A-214500681.html&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=5c2942dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%AE%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%9F%E7%A3%9A-214500681.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bUzy8Xma2uE0afjBZ0pohw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/928f414843cd0117ac7b260a398c286b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbUzy8Xma2uE0afjBZ0pohw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F928f414843cd0117ac7b260a398c286b&h=df734e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃定光聲稱曾在短片中見到有示威者冒充記者向警員掟磚。（陳章存攝）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港四個多月以來示威衝突混亂場面不斷，傳媒採訪時屢被警員質疑身份。身兼立法會《禁止蒙面規例》小組委員會主席的進出口界立法會議員黃定光昨在電台節目中表示，曾於網上片段中見到有身穿反光衣的示威者假扮記者，並向警員投擲磚頭，認為警方有需要去確認記者身份。<br />\n<br />\n指警方有需要辨別身份<br />\n<br />\n政府早前引用《緊急法》訂立禁蒙面法，列明「因從事專業或受僱工作」的人士可獲豁免，保安局局長李家超亦公開表明記者包括在內。黃定光昨表示，現時有人冒充記者，警方有需要辨別記者身份，又稱他曾經在網上片段見過有示威者假扮記者，身穿反光衣向警員投擲磚頭，直言︰「着衫係記者，剝衫係暴徒。」<br />\n<br />\n至於周日有警員扯開記者面罩一事，黃則表示不評論事件，但重申警方有執法權，若有人在公眾活動中作出不合理或違法行為，引起警方懷疑，警方要求對方卸下面罩是「無可厚非」。他續指，實際上《禁止蒙面規例》並無列明記者可獲豁免的權利，只是政府曾指記者因工作關係而可獲豁免。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來有醒過架<br />\n喬妝警呢又見唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc816e3fd92eea1b5a9cb03aa84ad58e9ca33846","tid":1680580,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d4488b630f3ac795736a0bb9ab72a1126ef5b9d2","tid":1680580,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLdavJJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLdavJJ.gif&h=943b7306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aa6baad936c33e50f9e5abbd4812aef3b6b09b2","tid":1680580,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"101 槍殺人 11月1 一個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1c0b036b4a68acc38e83830cd53904431711332","tid":1680580,"uid":62321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"我反而見過制服警掟磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0211f0eb1a608fbb97b3e87da516578a3bc1994","tid":1680580,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"我係網上片段都見過有狗扮示威者掟汽油彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad21c8ae807ac6fa2e207f64dfcfc7514613dbe3","tid":1680580,"uid":116289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCvwfq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%